Source: ubuntu-docs
Section: text
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Enrico Zini <enrico@debian.org>
Build-Depends-Indep: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), cdbs, xsltproc, docbook-xsl, perl, perl-modules, poxml
Standards-Version: 3.6.1.0

Package: ubuntu-docs
Architecture: all
Depends: scrollkeeper
Recommends: yelp
Conflicts: ubuntu-quickguide (<< 0.3)
Description: The Ubuntu Quick Guide
 The package holds the ubuntu official handbook, created by the
 Ubuntu Documentation Team.
 .
 The handbook can be viewed using Yelp the GNOME help browser, or
 stand-alone in HTML or PDF format.

Package: ubuntu-quickguide
Architecture: all
Depends: scrollkeeper, ubuntu-docs
Recommends: yelp
Description: The Ubuntu Quick Guide
 The package holds the Ubuntu Quick Guide created by the Ubuntu
 Documentation Team.
 .
 The Quick Guide is a pocket book containing a short tour of the Ubuntu
 distribution and the applications inside it.
 .
 The guide can be viewed using Yelp the GNOME help browser, or
 stand-alone in HTML or PDF format.
